WorkItem.Description:
Currently it is not possible to use variables in media queries, e.g.

@gp_mobileScreenWidth: 960px;
@media screen and (max-width: @gp_mobileScreenWidth) {}

Will in less render as:

@media screen and (max-width: @gp_mobileScreenWidth) {}

But it should render:

@media screen and (max-width: 960px) {}

Looks like this was already fixed in dotless:
https://github.com/dotless/dotless/issues/105

Any chance of integrating this fix in chirpy?
